decorations_added: Transform this bathroom into a haunted Halloween scene with: fake cobwebs draped across corners and over the shower fixtures with black spiders, eerie red and green atmospheric lighting, fake blood splatters on the tiled walls and sink (washable), plastic spiders and rats scattered on the floor, gauzy tattered fabric over the window creating a ghostly effect, a fake bloody hand emerging from the sink drain, creepy potion bottles with colored liquid on the sink edge, cobwebs around the toilet area, and dim spooky lighting creating an unsettling haunted bathroom atmosphere
